---
// Shows a signal trace crossing a slit in the reference plane.
// Return current is forced to detour around the slit → huge loop + EMI
---
<figure class="not-prose rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 480 240" class="w-full" role="img" aria-label="Split plane — 신호가 slit 을 건널 때">
    <!-- dielectric/board background -->
    <rect x="1" y="1" width="478" height="238" fill="#fafaf9" stroke="#e2e8f0" />

    <!-- reference plane with slit -->
    <rect x="20"  y="110" width="200" height="20" fill="#cbd5e1" stroke="#94a3b8" />
    <rect x="260" y="110" width="200" height="20" fill="#cbd5e1" stroke="#94a3b8" />
    <!-- slit gap -->
    <rect x="220" y="110" width="40"  height="20" fill="#fee2e2" stroke="#f87171" stroke-dasharray="3 2" />
    <text x="228" y="124" font-size="9" fill="#991b1b" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">SLIT</text>
    <text x="290" y="150" font-size="9" fill="#64748b" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">GND plane</text>

    <!-- driver/receiver pads -->
    <rect x="20"  y="60" width="32" height="20" fill="#0f172a" />
    <text x="24"  y="74" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">DRV</text>
    <rect x="428" y="60" width="32" height="20" fill="#0f172a" />
    <text x="432" y="74" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">RX</text>

    <!-- signal trace crossing the slit (top) -->
    <line x1="52"  y1="70" x2="428" y2="70" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="2.5" />
    <polygon points="424,66 432,70 424,74" fill="#f43f5e" />
    <text x="210" y="60" font-size="10" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">signal →</text>

    <!-- return path — forced to detour around slit -->
    <path d="M 428 120 L 262 120 L 262 180 L 218 180 L 218 120 L 52 120"
          fill="none" stroke="#f43f5e" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-dasharray="5 3" />
    <polygon points="58,116 50,120 58,124" fill="#f43f5e" />
    <text x="210" y="200" font-size="10" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">← return (slit 을 우회)</text>

    <!-- extra loop area highlight -->
    <path d="M 218 120 L 262 120 L 262 180 L 218 180 Z" fill="#fecaca" opacity="0.5" />

    <!-- annotations -->
    <g font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" font-size="10">
      <text x="8"   y="20" fill="#9f1239">문제: return 전류가 slit 을 건너지 못해 크게 돌아감</text>
      <text x="8"   y="35" fill="#64748b">→ 루프 면적 급증 → 고주파 L ↑ → radiation / crosstalk / SI 파괴</text>
    </g>

    <!-- fix hint -->
    <g font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" font-size="10">
      <text x="8" y="222" fill="#065f46">해결책: ① slit 피해 라우팅 · ② slit 건너는 지점에 stitching cap · ③ plane 을 split 하지 말기</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
</figure>
